dependencies:

    to run you need xinput

instructions:

    open a teminal

    $ xinput list

    find the devices you want to record in the listing

    record there id numbers

    navagate to the prject directory

    $ ./multicap id [id, [ ... ]]

    now multicap is spewing info into stdout

    to make a csv

    $ ./multicap args >> file.csv

    to stop recording CTR-C, ^C, SIGINT.

    dont kill with SIGTERM unless you want a mess



